(gen_random_uuid(), '726a4454-a597-49f4-a4e6-42be6ba3da84', '🏆 SUMMER NEON CHALLENGE ENTRY! 🏆\n\nChallenge was to create the brightest, most eye-catching neon design... I think I nailed it! 💥 Used 6 different neon gel polishes with glow-in-the-dark top coat. Each nail has a different geometric pattern inspired by 80s Memphis design.\n\nTook 3 hours and my client LOVES them! Perfect for festival season 🎪 Who else is joining the challenge?\n\n#SummerNeonChallenge #NeonNails #FestivalNails #GeometricNails #80sVibes', 'challenge', 'nails', ARRAY['neon-challenge', 'neon-nails', 'festival-nails'], ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1649972904349-6e44c42644a7'], 167, 45, false, NOW() - INTERVAL '2 days'),

(gen_random_uuid(), '726a4454-a597-49f4-a4e6-42be6ba3da84', 'SMOKY EYE CHALLENGE SUBMISSION! 👁️‍🗨️\n\nThe challenge: Create a wearable smoky eye using ONLY drugstore products under $50 total. Here''s my look using:\n\n• L''Oreal eyeshadow palette ($12)\n• Maybelline gel liner ($8)  \n• CoverGirl mascara ($7)\n• ELF brushes ($15)\n\nTotal: $42! Proof you don''t need expensive makeup to create stunning looks. Technique > tools always! 💪\n\n#DrugstoreChallenge #SmokyEye #BudgetBeauty #MakeupChallenge', 'challenge', 'makeup', ARRAY['drugstore-challenge', 'smoky-eye', 'budget-beauty'], ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158'], 203, 68, false, NOW() - INTERVAL '8 days');

